comments: Hayward (CHA) beats Kuminga (GSW) to the spot and absorbs the contact to his front on his driving shot attempt.
Green (GSW) initiates contact with Plumlee (CHA) that affects his SQBR as he attempts to make the pass.
Rozier (CHA) brings his arm toward Poole's (GSW) path and marginal contact occurs at the start of Poole's (GSW) drive.
Green (GSW) establishes himself in Rozier's (CHA) path and his legs remain within the frame of his body as contact occurs, which he does not deliver.
Green (GSW) establishes himself in Rozier's (CHA) path and does not deliver illegal contact as the dribble hand-off is set.
Kuminga (GSW) reaches in and makes contact to Ball's (CHA) front and affects his SQBR.
Ball (CHA) is moving alongside Thompson's (GSW) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
Rozier (CHA) briefly extends both hands to Poole (GSW) and marginal contact occurs as he releases the pass.
Kuminga (GSW) briefly brings both hands to Ball (CHA) and marginal contact occurs at the start of his drive.
Poole (GSW) briefly extends his hand to Ball's (CHA) front and marginal contact occurs during his driving shot attempt.
Ball (CHA) initiates contact with Poole's (GSW) head during the drive and affects his SQBR.
Hayward (CHA) commits a take foul on Thompson (GSW).
Kuminga (GSW) is moving alongside Ball's (CHA) path and marginal body contact occurs during Ball's (CHA) drive.
